org.marinemc.plugins

Class Plugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.marinemc.plugins.Plugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PluginMain

    public class Plugin
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandProvider
    Plugins will need to implement this class in order to be loaded.

    Use the methods in here, rather than any external methods that do the same thing, as these are optimized for use in plugins, and will make sure that nothing breaks.
